<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport" />
  <title>Auras International</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css" />
  <script type="text/javascript">
    (function () {
      emailjs.init("<%= process.env.EMAIL_JS %>");
    })();
  </script>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("partials/header") %>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="hero-fade-overlay"></div>

      <div class="hero-images">
        <img src="images/hero.png" class="hero-bg active" alt="Hero Image 1" />
        <img src="images/hero2.png" class="hero-bg" alt="Hero Image 2" />
        <img src="images/hero3.png" class="hero-bg" alt="Hero Image 3" />
        <img src="images/hero4.png" class="hero-bg" alt="Hero Image 4" />
      </div>

      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Crafting Identity Through Every Stitch</h1>
        <p>HAND EMBROIDERED EXCELLENCE FOR GLOBAL FASHION HOUSES</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        Auras International is a global embroidery house specialising in
        handcrafted beading and embellishment—delivering precision, artistry,
        and a timeless impact to fashion brands worldwide.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="image-grid">
      <div class="grid-box">
        <div class="grid animate">
          <img class="sustainable" src="images/sustainable.png" alt="Bridal" />
          <h3>SUSTAINABLE</h3>
          <p>
            We create beauty with purpose. Fashion isn’t just about the final
            piece—it’s about how it’s made.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-box">
        <div class="grid animate">
          <img class="global" src="images/global.png" alt="Interiors" />
          <h3>GLOBAL</h3>
          <p>
            We collaborate with leading designers arounds the world, treating
            each partnership with the same care.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-box">
        <div class="grid animate">
          <img class="reliable" src="images/reliable.png" alt="Accessories" />
          <h3>RELIABLE</h3>
          <p>
            We are all about trust, precision and consistency, with our
            specialised touch to everything we do.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
      <div class="main-title1">Our Services</div>
      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-cards">
          <div class="card">
            <img class="dress" src="images/dress.png" alt="Bridal" />
            <p>Bridal & Evening Couture</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <img class="chair" src="images/chair.png" alt="Interiors" />
            <p>Interiors & Soft Furnishings</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <img class="purse" src="images/purse.png" alt="Accessories" />
            <p>Accessories & Custom Orders</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="portfolio">
      <div class="portfolio-left">
        <h3>Explore Our Work</h3>
        <div class="main-title">PORTFOLIO</div>
        <a href="/our-work.html" class="view-btn">VIEW MORE</a>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-right">
        <img src="images/explore1.png" class="portfolio-img active" alt="Showcase 1" />
        <img src="images/explore2.png" class="portfolio-img" alt="Showcase 2" />
        <img src="images/explore3.png" class="portfolio-img" alt="Showcase 3" />
        <img src="images/explore4.png" class="portfolio-img" alt="Showcase 4" />
        <img src="images/explore5.png" class="portfolio-img" alt="Showcase 5" />
        <img src="images/explore6.png" class="portfolio-img" alt="Showcase 6" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial Heading Section -->
    <section class="testimonial-heading">
      <div>
        Trusted by global fashion houses and boutique ateliers alike, we partner
        with discerning brands worldwide.
      </div>
      <p>Here’s what some of our clients say about working with us:</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial Carousel Section -->
    <section class="testimonial-carousel">
      <div class="testimonial-slide active">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "Working with AURAS has been seamless from concept to delivery. Their
          understanding of couture detailing and ability to translate abstract
          briefs into embroidery is exceptional. A trusted extension of our
          design team."
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Creative Director, Luxury Bridal House (North America)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "They bring a rare mix of artistry and accountability. Every detail is
          thought through, every stitch intentional. AURAS is not just a vendor
          - they're our embroidery partner of choice."
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Design Director, Evening wear Brand (North America)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "What stands out with AURAS is not just the finesse of the needlework,
          but the consistency of quality and delivery. They've become a
          behind-the-scenes partner we deeply rely on."
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Studio Buyer, Contemporary Evening wear Label (Israel)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "Their handwork is refined, their finishes are precise, and their
          attitude is always solution-oriented. Quietly elegant, professionally
          grounded - just what we needed."
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Production Manager, Bespoke Atelier (South of Italy)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "Everything is perfect. From stitch quality to the silent
          understanding of couture timelines.”
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author"><em>AURAS delivers</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          Working with AURAS INTERNATIONAL has been a seamless and inspiring
          experience. Their attention to detail, commitment to craftsmanship,
          and understanding of our design language has elevated every
          collection. From complex hand-embroidery to intricate sampling, they
          deliver with consistency, heart, and high standards — making them an
          invaluable partner for us.”
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>President of Couture Luxury Brand (Canada)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          “For our label rooted in heritage and opulence, AURAS INTERNATIONAL
          has been a true creative ally. Their mastery in hand embroidery and
          their ability to translate mood boards into soulful, luxurious pieces
          has brought our collections to life. They understand the language of
          luxury.”
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Head of Design, Fashion House (Middle East)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          “Working with AURAS INTERNATIONAL has been a rare and valuable
          experience. Their embroidery expertise, eye for detail, and ability to
          interpret the creative world of Parisian fashion are exceptional.
          Every piece created with them carries a soul, a hand, a story.”
        </p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">
          <em>Creative Director of Couture House (France)</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Add more slides here -->

      <div class="testimonial-nav">
        <button class="testimonial-prev">&#8592;</button>
        <button class="testimonial-next">&#8594;</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <div class="contact-container">
        <div class="contact-text">
          <div class="main-title">Contact Us</div>
          <p>
            Are you ready to begin your embroidery journey?<br />
            Let's talk.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-form">
          <form>
            <div class="form-input">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" id="name" required />
              <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" id="email" required />
            </div>
            <textarea placeholder="Message" id="message" required></textarea>
            <div class="button-wrapper">
              <button onclick="sendMail()" type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
      <script src="/js/sendEmail.js"></script>
      <script src="js/index.js"></script>
      <script src="js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>